              >If you care
              <img src="/img/arrow-right.svg" alt="" />
            </span>
          </span>
        </a>
        <h2 class="p-top-cta__title c-heading c-heading--black">still here?</h2>
        <h3 class="p-top-cta__lead p-top-cta__lead-top c-lead c-lead--black">
          (guess i was a bit harsh.)
        </h3>
        <div class="l-image p-top-cta__image">
          <img src="" alt="" />
        </div>
        <p class="p-top-cta__text c-text c-text--black">
          Honestly… that feels really nice.
          <br />If you’d like, we could build something together.
        </p>
